TI  - Tree-Based Clock Distribution of Multiple-Stage Pipelined Architecture in Rapid Single-Flux-Quantum Circuits
PY  - 2022
T2  - IEEE Transactions on Computer-Aided Design of Integrated Circuits and Systems
VL  - 41
IS  - 4
SP  - 1090
EP  - 1102
