TI  - Via-Minimization-Oriented Region Routing under Length-Matching Constraints in Rapid Single-Flux-Quantum Circuits
PY  - 2021
T2  - IEEE Transactions on Very Large Scale Integration (VLSI) Systems
VL  - 29
IS  - 6
C7  - 9366738
SP  - 1257
