TI  - Efficient Ground-State Recovery of UV-Photoexcited p-Nitrophenol in Aqueous Solution by Direct and Multistep Pathways
PY  - 2024
T2  - Journal of the American Chemical Society
VL  - 146
IS  - 44
SP  - 30443
