TI  - Defining Intermediates of Nitrogenase MoFe Protein during N2Reduction under Photochemical Electron Delivery from CdS Quantum Dots
PY  - 2020
T2  - Journal of the American Chemical Society
VL  - 142
IS  - 33
SP  - 14324
