TI  - Solid-state NMR characterization of paramagnetic bis(L-valinato)copper(II) stereoisomers - Effect of conformational disorder and molecular mobility on 13C and 2H fast magic-angle spinning spectra
PY  - 2014
T2  - European Journal of Inorganic Chemistry
IS  - 21
SP  - 3330
EP  - 3340
