TI  - Metabolic assessment of human liver transplants from biopsy samples at donor and recipient stages using high-resolution magic angle spinning 1H NMR spectroscopy
PY  - 2005
T2  - Analytical Chemistry
VL  - 77
IS  - 17
SP  - 5570
EP  - 5578
